<div class="story"> <p>Sea Dunes is a town house community across the street from the Atlantic Ocean in Kitty Hawk with 13 buildings sharing 82 units. Each unit has 2 or three bedrooms with a garage. Sea Dunes is an amenity rich community with a large Community Pool, Spa, Tennis Court, Basketball Court, Fitness Center, Racquet Ball Court, Video Games, on site management, Club House and a Private Beach Access. You will find Sea Dunes in between the subdivisions of <a href="https://www.outerbankshome.com/outer banks/real estate/KittyHawk/kitty-hawk-beach.asp" title="Kitty Hawk Beach">Kitty Hawk Beach</a> and the <a href="https://www.outerbankshome.com/outer banks/real estate/KittyHawk/hurdle-estate.asp" title="Hurdle Estate">Hurdle Estate</a>. </p>  
